# Terraform
**/.terraform/*
*.tfstate
*.tfstate.*
*.tfplan
tfplan
**/tfplan
crash.log
crash.*.log
override.tf
override.tf.json
*_override.tf
*_override.tf.json
.terraformrc
terraform.rc
# Regenerated by `terraform init` locally; deliberately not tracked (see
# past "Delete environments/dev/.terraform.lock.hcl" history) so it stops
# reappearing as an untracked file after every local init.
.terraform.lock.hcl

# Never commit real variable values that could contain subscription/env secrets
*.auto.tfvars
*.auto.tfvars.json
!terraform.tfvars

# Tooling
.tflint.d/
.checkov_report*
tfsec-results*

# OS / editor
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.vscode/
.idea/
